{"tid":2209553,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蘋果A1: 世間無窮翰墨手 一紙自由寫不成","createTime":"2020-09-19T17:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T15:27:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1a3903b8a6e9ad3d63c339613e1b998bafdb1732","tid":2209553,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T17:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/119621778_10159462794232448_3414756652290814673_o.png?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=ADiNJoL5mZ0AX8aBA06&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=5c0e26bb67942e3cc4269e44da714d3c&amp;oe=5F8CFCFA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F119621778_10159462794232448_3414756652290814673_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DADiNJoL5mZ0AX8aBA06%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26oh%3D5c0e26bb67942e3cc4269e44da714d3c%26oe%3D5F8CFCFA&h=2aaf4deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下是廣告創作者的訊息：<br />\n☓ ☓ ☓ ☓ ☓ ☓ ☓ ☓ ☓ ☓ ☓<br />\n大家好，我係創作者，想簡單向大家略說，「世間無窮翰墨手，一紙自由寫不成。」背後的想法和意思。<br />\n此詩實為略改唐代高蟾《金陵晚望》，「曾伴浮雲歸晚翠，猶陪落日泛秋聲。世間無限丹青手，一片傷心畫不成。」賞析可見於此：<a href=\"https://fanti.dugushici.com/mingju/10123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffanti.dugushici.com%2Fmingju%2F10123&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=02ef5bcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fanti.dugushici.com/mingju/10123</a><br />\n簡單而言，高氏有見唐朝危機四伏，快將走向末日，為此極為憂心。<br />\n小弟略將「丹青手」改為「翰墨手」，泛指所有以文字書畫為生或揸筆搵食之人，「一片」改為「一紙」，「傷心」則改為「自由」以強調「新聞自由」之重要。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/posts/10159462796227448?comment_id=10159462865702448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fposts%2F10159462796227448%3Fcomment_id%3D10159462865702448&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=4bb3dd0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/posts/10159462796227448?comment_id=10159462865702448</a>"},{"pid":"1f2271fc512f8e61d545843deb76010a76346dc4","tid":2209553,"uid":201359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T17:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4ad53c03da2201e4583df690059aa31a237190","tid":2209553,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f2271fc512f8e61d545843deb76010a76346dc4","tid":2209553,"uid":201359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T17:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T17:33:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fb5e09c23068a500fd956708c06b6acc8b9bb5","tid":2209553,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ad4ad53c03da2201e4583df690059aa31a237190","tid":2209553,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f2271fc512f8e61d545843deb76010a76346dc4","tid":2209553,"uid":201359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T17:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/