意思。<br />\n此詩實為略改唐代高蟾《金陵晚望》，「曾伴浮雲歸晚翠，猶陪落日泛秋聲。世間無限丹青手，一片傷心畫不成。」賞析可見於此：<a href=\"https://fanti.dugushici.com/mingju/10123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffanti.dugushici.com%2Fmingju%2F10123&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=02ef5bcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fanti.dugushici.com/mingju/10123</a><br />\n簡單而言，高氏有見唐朝危機四伏，快將走向末日，為此極為憂心。<br />\n小弟略將「丹青手」改為「翰墨手」，泛指所有以文字書畫為生或揸筆搵食之人，「一片」改為「一紙」，「傷心」則改為「自由」以強調「新聞自由」之重要。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/posts/10159462796227448?comment_id=10159462865702448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fposts%2F10159462796227448%3Fcomment_id%3D10159462865702448&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE77WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=4bb3dd0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/posts/10159462796227448?comment_id=10159462865702448</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T17:36:31.000Z","msg":"樹仁大學真係人材輩出<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e847f5705845ab29277d46d054e281d758e54959","tid":2209553,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fc0c35d7ba79840e1016dde0d8dca2c7538e389c","tid":2209553,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"17fb5e09c23068a500fd956708c06b6acc8b9bb5","tid":2209553,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ad4ad53c03da2201e4583df690059aa31a237190","tid":2209553,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T17:33:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f