ji\" />好句"},{"pid":"d044dc36e49ea7fc0c021c0ef6c7176876b93cb1","tid":2209553,"uid":198181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T23:30:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197f189a28d28df801e33cea8fc23c7e735e52ea","tid":2209553,"uid":281652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T00:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5dece178f637cc66f9481dbdf39332823c9d73","tid":2209553,"uid":255970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T02:58:23.000Z","msg":"但呢兩句表達嘅文意唔係好通喎。<br />\n<br />\n原句「世間無窮丹青手，一片傷心寫不完」<br />\n<br />\n原意係指，皇朝危機四伏（原詩頭兩句帶出嚟嘅意境），為臣者（即係作者）嘅憂愁，非一眾弄墨好手能夠形容。<br />\n<br />\n如果跟住上面嘅思路去理解「世間無窮翰墨手，一紙自由寫不成」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">咁個意思就應該係：香港淪亡，世上無數文人、記者（翰墨者），但連小小嘅言論自由都不能見諸刊文之上？我解唔通。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n定係樓主純粹攞咗原句嘅字，而文意思路唔跟返原句？<br />\n<br />\n求解答。"},{"pid":"706c482955acccb9a7b9e7f46116462a36e872f8","tid":2209553,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eeed223f5faf864cfa26f28f21c4f68dbceb174","tid":2209553,"uid":290443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T09:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}